HEADWORD: Pteron
<hw>Pte"ron</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <?/ a
wing.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The region of the skull, in the
